channel.title: Rain Meter Skin of the Month!
channel.description:
[align=center][url='https://rainmeter.deviantart.com/journal/poll/1490716/'][img]https://img835.imageshack.us/img835/6338/ss20101004144642.png[/img][/url][/align] Hey everyone my most recent rainmeter configuration the "[b]Alive Clock: A clock for humans.[/b]" was entered into the official Rainmeter Skin of the Month Poll. There is no way in hell that I will win this thing (my lonly config competing with full desktop replacements) but I would appreciate if you have a deviant art account showing your support. (would be cool to place not in last :stuck_out_tongue: )
[url='https://rainmeter.deviantart.com/journal/poll/1490716/']DA POLL HERE[/url]
